      "description": "Life Drain.\n\nConstitution Saving Throw: DC [[lookup @save.dc.value activity=FA4Mt9cXsYfHDDcs]], one [[lookup @target.affects.type activity=FA4Mt9cXsYfHDDcs]] within [[lookup @range.value activity=FA4Mt9cXsYfHDDcs]] feet.\n\nFailure: [[/damage average]] damage, and the target's Hit Point maximum decreases by an amount equal to the damage taken.\n\nA Humanoid slain by this attack rises 24 hours later as a Zombie under the [[lookup @name lowercase]]{monster}'s control, unless the Humanoid is restored to life or its body is destroyed. The [[lookup @name lowercase]]{monster} can have no more than twelve zombies under its control at a time.",
